I"r<p>Statistics for Google Summer of Code 2020 are out, and we have a reason to celebrate. IIT Kanpur ranked 2nd worldwide in the list of universities with the most accepted students. The list is available <a href="https://opensource.googleblog.com/2020/08/google-summer-of-code-2020-statistics.html">here</a>.</p>

<p>Our numbers have been increasing steadily over the last few years, as you can see in the table below:</p>

